            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="security-grid">
            <div class="security-item">
              <span class="item-icon">🔐</span>
              <div>
                <strong>私鑰隔離</strong>
                <p>私鑰只存在 USB，電腦硬碟上無任何痕跡</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="security-item">
              <span class="item-icon">🧠</span>
              <div>
                <strong>記憶體保護</strong>
                <p>mlock + SecureZero，防止私鑰被換出或殘留</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="security-item">
              <span class="item-icon">🔑</span>
              <div>
                <strong>密碼不落地</strong>
                <p>密碼永不儲存，每次操作重新輸入</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="security-item">
              <span class="item-icon">⏱️</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Session 時效控制</strong>
                <p>閒置自動鎖定，降低被竊取風險</p>
